SUMMARY:Pro Jam with Special Guest Johnny Rawls
DESCRIPTION:Soul Blues legend Johnny Rawls returns to The California as part of our popular Blue Mondays series\nSoul Blues legend Johnny Rawls is an internationally recognized recording artist\, music producer and songwriter. Over his 50-year career\, Johnny has been showered with Blues Music Awards\, Blues Blast Awards\, Living Blues Awards and the W.C. Handy Awards\, including Soul Blues Album of the Year and Soul Blues Artist of the Year.Blues Defenders hosts a weekly concert with headliners and swing dancing. Followed by Pro Jam.\nDoors open at 5pm Show Starts at 6pm. \nTickets for this special Pro Jam event are $17 online and $20 at door. $14 for members.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/pro-jam-with-special-guest-johnny-rawls/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
