SUMMARY:Hardly Strictly Irish at Hopmonk Sonoma!
DESCRIPTION:St. Paddy’s Day\, done right! Enjoy live music\, fantastic food\, and drinks on the Hopmonk’s verdant patio in downtown Sonoma! \nHARDLY STRICTLY IRISH (Suzuki Cady & Jimmy Murphy) play lovely\, lively traditional Irish tunes and sing soulful songs from a variety of genres on fiddle\, mandolin\, guitar\, and bodhrán. \n“A new\, local band is rocking the Bay Area—to high acclaim…They are commensurate acoustic musicians with decades of experience between them.” – Mark Fernquest\, Sebastopol Times \nHARDLY STRICTLY IRISH: suzukicady.com/hardly-strictly-irish\nVIDEOS: suzukicady.com/videos\nSHOWS: suzukicady.com/events\nPRESS: suzukicady.com/press
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/hardly-strictly-irish-at-hopmonk-sonoma/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sonoma\, 691 Broadway\, Sonoma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
