SUMMARY:Live Music Happy Hour - Ken Risling with Avery & Oona!
DESCRIPTION:Downtown Santa Rosa ‘Golden Hour’ 4-7p| Live music 5-7 p | $6 beers & $2 off wine |Tuesday-Saturday!\nFor people who like to party…but want to be home at a reasonable hour…\nKen Risling with Avery & Oona – 3rd Tuesdays!\nEvenings of covers & originals.\nA musician since birth\, Ken has played many instruments in many genres. His first songs were written while in high school\, but he began writing in earnest at the tender age of 45. He writes for himself and also with an ear to other performers. His songs have won numerous awards and airplay. Whenever he can\, he performs with his favorite artists.\n21+\nHappy Hour Pricing 4-6pm\nAll beers – $6 + $2 off wine.\nLive Music 5-7pm\n2 drink minimum\, please\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/live-music-happy-hour-ken-risling-with-avery-oona-2/2026-03-17/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
