SUMMARY:The Gentlemen Soldiers at The Block
DESCRIPTION:+Smoked Corned Beef and Cabbage while supplies last \nGentlemen Soldiers return to Sonoma County for 2025’s St. Paddy’s Day Weekend! Celebrating the holiday festivities and the 1-year birthday of their eponymous debut album\, Gentlemen Soldiers are an ensemble of Sonoma County musicians that deliver an energetic and modern but poignant take on traditional Irish music. Drawing inspiration from their musical upbringings in the realms of folk\, rock and punk music\, their sound is one of camaraderie. Their songs will both taunt and cheer you in an uncanny way that only Celtic influenced music can. Stay for a pint\, raise your glass and shout a “Sláinte” with Gentlemen Soldiers!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-gentlemen-soldiers-at-the-block/
LOCATION:The Block Petaluma\, 20 Grey Street\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Holiday,Music
GEO:38.236416;-122.638896
