SUMMARY:Live Music Happy Hour - Encore Highway Plays Your Favorites!
DESCRIPTION:Every third Wednesday Encore Highway plays during Downtown Santa Rosa ‘Golden Hour’ 4-7p | Live music 5-7 p | $6 beers & $2 off wine\nDowntown Santa Rosa ‘Golden Hour’ 4-7p | Live music 5-7 p | $6 beers & $2 off wine |Tuesday-Saturday!\nFor people who like to party…but want to be home at a reasonable hour…\nEncore Highway\n“Singing songs old and new\, spiced with jazz and a country tune or two!”\nIf you like songs by Bob Dylan\, Joan Baez\, Rolling Stones\, Jason Mraz\, Elvis\, Elton John\, Keb’ Mo’ & more you’ll love Encore Highway!\n21+ Happy Hour Pricing 4-7pm All beers – $6 All wine – $2 off Live Music 5-7pm 2 drink minimum\, please\nFree popcorn!\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/live-music-happy-hour-encore-highway-plays-your-favorites-2/2026-03-18/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
